1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,059
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:05,300
=Episode 27=

3
00:00:05,420 --> 00:00:09,420
(Nine Months Later)

4
00:00:13,660 --> 00:00:15,099
By the Mandate of Heaven,

5
00:00:15,100 --> 00:00:17,419
the Emperor hereby decrees.

6
00:00:17,420 --> 00:00:19,520
Prince Jing, Xiao Heng
is virtuous and accomplished,

7
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:20,739
with great merit to the realm.

8
00:00:20,740 --> 00:00:22,899
From this day forth,
he is appointed Crown Prince

9
00:00:22,900 --> 00:00:24,779
and shall enter the Eastern Palace.

10
00:00:24,780 --> 00:00:27,819
Long live His Highness the Crown Prince!

11
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:31,120
Princess Xiao Suisui of Prince Jing Manor
is clever and bright,

12
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,280
blessed with profound fortune.

13
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:34,979
From this day forth, she is bestowed
the title of Lucky Star Princess

14
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:36,920
and shall receive double
the stipend of a princess.

15
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:38,540
By imperial decree.

16
00:00:38,580 --> 00:00:42,260
Long live the Lucky Star Princess!

17
00:00:42,340 --> 00:00:43,379
My beloved officials,

18
00:00:43,380 --> 00:00:44,579
rise.

19
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:46,300
Thank you, Your Majesty.

20
00:00:49,660 --> 00:00:51,099
Why did you bring that to court?

21
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:52,459
It's such a joyous day.

22
00:00:52,460 --> 00:00:54,220
We need some music for the occasion.

23
00:00:54,380 --> 00:00:55,020
Hey.

24
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:07,820
Haha, not bad at all.

25
00:01:13,100 --> 00:01:14,179
You know,

26
00:01:14,180 --> 00:01:15,979
the more this girl plays,

27
00:01:15,980 --> 00:01:17,940
the more addictive it sounds.

28
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:22,219
Please continue taking care of me.

29
00:01:22,220 --> 00:01:24,820
All protection fees are discounted.

30
00:01:27,740 --> 00:01:29,820
My lord.

31
00:01:30,450 --> 00:01:31,339
Thank you, My Lord!

32
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:33,640
- Thank you, My Lord!
- Thank you, My Lord!

33
00:01:37,340 --> 00:01:38,340
Suisui!

34
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:39,460
Suisui!

35
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:40,260
Suisui!

36
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:41,579
It's Mother.

37
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:43,380
You... You remember, right?

38
00:01:43,540 --> 00:01:44,899
If we hadn't saved you back then,

39
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:46,979
you wouldn't have
the fortune you have today.

40
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:49,499
Suisui, you're a good child.

41
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,660
You know how to repay kindness, right?

42
00:01:52,020 --> 00:01:52,819
Right, Suisui?

43
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:56,780
Father, for great kind people like us,

44
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:59,460
what should we do
in a situation like this?

45
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:01,220
Help her?

46
00:02:02,140 --> 00:02:02,860
Mm.

47
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:06,899
This is your reward.

48
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:08,299
But don't get greedy.

49
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:09,939
I did a great deed today.

50
00:02:09,940 --> 00:02:12,980
Father will definitely reward me well
when we get back.

51
00:02:13,260 --> 00:02:14,260
Let's go.

52
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:16,419
Hey, Suisui!

53
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:17,420
Suisui!

54
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:23,700
Pretty Auntie!

55
00:02:27,380 --> 00:02:28,780
Little Princess.

56
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:30,819
Pretty Auntie.

57
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:32,499
Is the baby coming soon?

58
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:33,659
Very soon.

59
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:34,659
If it weren't for you,

60
00:02:34,660 --> 00:02:36,540
I would've lost my life.

61
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:38,180
Sigh.

62
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:43,659
This is just a little token from me.

63
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,579
From now on, however much grain
Prince Jing Manor needs, I'll provide it all.

64
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:47,659
Thank you, Pretty Auntie.

65
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:49,139
You're too kind.

66
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:50,219
It's only right.

67
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:51,819
Pretty Auntie, don't worry.

68
00:02:51,820 --> 00:02:53,379
Once the baby is born,

69
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:54,899
I'll be the baby's god-sister.

70
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:56,420
No protection fees at all.

71
00:02:57,340 --> 00:02:59,260
Alright.

72
00:03:00,020 --> 00:03:01,980
Father, let's go home.

73
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:07,420
Goodbye.

74
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:16,780
Start the chant!

75
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:17,899
The Princess is the earth!

76
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:18,939
The Princess is the sky!

77
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:20,699
The Princess
is three quarters of life itself!

78
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:21,880
(The Princess is the earth.
The Princess is the sky)

79
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:24,339
Today is a wonderful day.

80
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:26,180
I am happy!

81
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:30,379
Oh my, that sound.

82
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:31,620
Very nice.

83
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:46,020
Oh my, good fortune has arrived!

84
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:49,819
Father, I'm not a jinx.

85
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:51,059
I'm the Mystic Crow Lucky Star.

86
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:52,340
You really struck it rich.

87
00:03:53,020 --> 00:03:54,139
Suisui is right.

88
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:56,420
You are the little lucky star
Heaven gifted me.

89
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:57,419
Uncle Shiwan!

90
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:58,099
Yes?

91
00:03:58,100 --> 00:03:59,619
Is the braised pork ready yet?

92
00:03:59,620 --> 00:04:01,539
Oh my, more than just braised pork!

93
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:04,939
There's a whole table
full of delicious food, all your favorites.

94
00:04:04,940 --> 00:04:07,420
Charge!

95
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:20,079
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

96
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:23,919
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

97
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:27,439
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

98
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:30,400
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

99
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:34,919
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

100
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:38,680
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

101
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:42,079
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

102
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:46,120
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

103
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:55,399
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

104
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:59,039
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

105
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:02,759
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

106
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:06,399
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

107
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:10,079
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

108
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,999
♪Endlessly flowing♪

109
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:18,200
♪Good fortune♪
